  "detailed_description": "<h1>Collector's Edition</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844150/extras/64f0091ac15ef7ca91492a2b2cb0fffa.webp?t=1670373293\" width=605 height=61 /></span><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844150/extras/2fcfc31b019bac07fc2fc3d9b2910d11.avif?t=1670373293\" width=600 height=218 /></span><br>Play shooting games from the perspective of chariot and command view.<br>You will play a commander guarding the peace chariot, leading a row of charming but deadly crew to skillfully defeat the enemy, guard the town and resist alien invasion.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844150/extras/90028caa67cc44362098ad676738b9a4.avif?t=1670373293\" width=600 height=218 /></span><br>In order to deal with more and more difficult enemies, you need to buy cards, strengthen characters and upgrade chariots.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844150/extras/ccd1cb475196e3293fe3b3f6da684743.avif?t=1670373293\" width=600 height=218 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A commander with rich personality<br></li><li>Free skill combination and changeable tactics<br></li><li>Rich natural environment</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844150/extras/2fcfc31b019bac07fc2fc3d9b2910d11.avif?t=1670373293\" width=600 height=218 /></span><br>Play shooting games from the perspective of chariot and command view.<br>You will play a commander guarding the peace chariot, leading a row of charming but deadly crew to skillfully defeat the enemy, guard the town and resist alien invasion.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844150/extras/90028caa67cc44362098ad676738b9a4.avif?t=1670373293\" width=600 height=218 /></span><br>In order to deal with more and more difficult enemies, you need to buy cards, strengthen characters and upgrade chariots.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844150/extras/ccd1cb475196e3293fe3b3f6da684743.avif?t=1670373293\" width=600 height=218 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A commander with rich personality<br></li><li>Free skill combination and changeable tactics<br></li><li>Rich natural environment</li></ul>",
